Clone using git clone --recursive git://github.com/victoralex/web-dev-circle

To start the peerJS server run `cd node_modules/peer/bin && ./peerjs --port 9000 --key peerjs --allow_discovery`

Be sure to change the trackerIP, on line 14 in client.html from 192.168.105.40 to whatever your local network address is.
From your browser open client.html

On other machines (ideally, on the same network) open client.html and open the developer tools to watch for messages being transmitted peer to peer between each client.
